        {
            "title": "單車｜李思穎亞錦賽首奪金牌 周三轉戰強項全能賽",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"李思穎贏得亞錦賽捕捉賽金牌。單車總會圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/395b4e8b6cc9c4a7bb9cf93efa38670a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250224/_2025022409300293100.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">李思穎贏得亞錦賽捕捉賽金牌。單車總會圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>馬來西亞舉行的年亞洲場地單車錦標賽，港隊女將李思穎（Ceci）周日（2月23日）在女子精英組捕捉賽力壓東道主大馬及日本車手奪冠，首度在成年組贏得亞錦賽金牌。周三她還會參加強項全能賽，力爭再上頒獎台。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"李思穎贏得亞錦賽捕捉賽金牌。單車總會圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e5ee93bdb8d1cde65ba3fe6da6922232/2025-02/cyclee0223_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        李思穎贏得亞錦賽捕捉賽金牌。單車總會圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"李思穎贏得亞錦賽捕捉賽金牌。單車總會圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f76ff62c6be6d95a1f074d9b0dbb6d05/2025-02/cyclee0223_2_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        李思穎贏得亞錦賽捕捉賽金牌。單車總會圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p>今次捕捉賽，9位車手一同參加，經過10公里賽事之後，Ceci力壓主場的馬來西亞車手祖比爾(Nur Aisyah Mohamad Zubir)及日本水谷彩奈（Mizutani Ayana）率先衝線奪金。連同早前淘汰賽銀牌、團體追逐賽銅牌，李思穎單屆集齊金銀銅3色獎牌。這塊金牌，也是她在亞錦賽成人組首金。此前，她曾在2018年青年組捕捉賽奪冠，7年後終於在成年組相同項目封后。\n\n</p>\n<p>完成場地組3天比賽後，港隊累積1金2銀3銅。周三李思穎將參加全能賽，再次向著獎牌進發。\n\n</p>\n<p><br/>\n港隊亞洲場地單車錦標賽成績表： 1金2銀3銅\n\n</p>\n<p>精英組<br/>\n女子團體追逐賽銅牌　李思穎、楊倩玉、梁寶儀、梁穎儀<br/>\n女子捕捉賽金牌　李思穎<br/>\n女子淘汰賽銀牌　李思穎\n\n</p>\n<p>青年組<br/>\n男子團體追逐賽銅牌　馬繹斐、馬繹善、馬正匡及鄧昊軒<br/>\n男子捕捉賽銀牌　馬繹斐<br/>\n男子競輪賽銅牌　吳保利\n\n</p>\n<p>港隊亞洲場地單車錦標賽成績表：1金2銅\n\n</p>\n<p>精英組<br/>\n男女混合團體計時賽銅牌　劉允祐、繆正賢、伍柏亨、李思穎、梁穎儀、楊倩玉<br/>\n女子個人公路賽銅牌　李思穎\n\n</p>\n<p>青年組<br/>\n男子個人公路賽金牌　葉漢文\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054520/即時-體育-單車-李思穎亞錦賽首奪金牌-周三轉戰強項全能賽",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-24 09:36:21",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "珍惜生命│西貢男子車內燒炭 昏迷送院不治",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"男子車內燒炭自殺。梁國峰攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/82bcd79c028d34f9b2f611efd726996d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250224/_2025022409280939664.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">男子車內燒炭自殺。梁國峰攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>西貢北港路一個花場對開，今（24日）早上7時50分，花場職員發現一名年約60歲男子在七人車內昏迷不醒，報警求助。救援人員接報到場，在車內找到鐵鑊及炭，將他送往將軍澳醫院。惜經搶救後不治。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4099388/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員檢走一包炭。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/488767654216d740cecaf348642f95d1/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250224_090850989.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員檢走一包炭。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4099389/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"男子車內燒炭自殺。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1e973b8474e2988f88afccde2b881c7f/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250224_090850989_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男子車內燒炭自殺。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4099390/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"載炭的鐵鑊。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ffcc6342bfa9ca7a66cf2f966b54570d/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250224_090850989_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        載炭的鐵鑊。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4099391/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/761ac11f3ad5612d2388b6d45eb46511/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250224_090850989_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4099392/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f0893172260e54817764e0bf900a83de/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250224_090850989_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4099393/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0e84e3a19a72ee635eea4afed38c9ad6/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250224_090850989_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>據花場職員表示，昨晚已發現該部七人車泊在草坪，但不以為意，今早仍見七人車，遂行近查看，始發現一名男子倒臥車廂內。警方在車內檢獲遺書，有人透露受金錢問題困擾。其後警員檢走鐵鑊及一包炭。\n\n</p>\n<p>自殺求助熱線：<br/>\n「情緒通」精神健康支援熱線：18111 <br/>\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br/>\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br/>\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br/>\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br/>\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br/>\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br/>\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br/>\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open 噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
